---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '@components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';

// Generate static paths for all blog posts
export async function getStaticPaths() {
  const posts = [
    {
      slug: "5-ai-prompts-every-professional-needs-to-master-in-2024",
      title: "5 AI Prompts Every Professional Needs to Master in 2024",
      description: "Discover the five essential AI prompts that can transform your daily workflow and save hours of work.",
      category: "Productivity",
      readTime: "8 min read",
      date: "March 28, 2026",
      author: {
        name: "Alex Mitchell",
        role: "Productivity Consultant",
        avatar: "AM"
      }
    },
    {
      slug: "how-i-cut-my-reporting-time-by-80-percent-using-chatgpt",
      title: "How I Cut My Reporting Time by 80% Using ChatGPT",
      description: "A real case study showing exactly how one professional transformed their reporting workflow with AI.",
      category: "Case Study",
      readTime: "10 min read",
      date: "March 25, 2026",
      author: {
        name: "Sarah Chen",
        role: "Marketing Director",
        avatar: "SC"
      }
    },
    {
      slug: "building-an-ai-powered-workflow-a-step-by-step-implementation-guide",
      title: "Building an AI-Powered Workflow: A Step-by-Step Implementation Guide",
      description: "A comprehensive guide to implementing AI into your daily workflow for maximum productivity.",
      category: "Tutorial",
      readTime: "12 min read",
      date: "March 22, 2026",
      author: {
        name: "James Wilson",
        role: "Workflow Designer",
        avatar: "JW"
      }
    }
  ];

  return posts.map((post) => ({
    params: { slug: post.slug },
    props: { post },
  }));
}

const { post } = Astro.props;
const { slug } = Astro.params;

const title = `${post.title} | Zero Method Blog`;
const description = post.description;
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <Header />

  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-16">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-navy-900/50 via-navy-950 to-navy-950"></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mb-8">
          <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center text-navy-400 hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
            </svg>
            Back to Blog
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-gold-500 bg-gold-500/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4">
            {post.category}
          </span>
          <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
            {post.title}
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-navy-400">{post.description}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-between py-6 border-y border-navy-800">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-400 to-gold-600 flex items-center justify-center text-navy-900 font-bold">
              {post.author.avatar}
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <p class="text-white font-medium">{post.author.name}</p>
              <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm">{post.author.role}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-navy-500 text-sm">
            <span>{post.date}</span>
            <span class="mx-2">•</span>
            <span>{post.readTime}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Content -->
    <section class="pb-20">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <article class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
          <!-- Featured Image -->
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-800 to-navy-700 rounded-2xl mb-12 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-8xl">🚀</span>
          </div>

          <p class="text-xl text-navy-300 leading-relaxed">
            I've been using AI tools for over a year now, but it wasn't until I implemented a structured prompt system that things actually changed. In this post, I'm breaking down exactly how I saved 12 hours in my first week—and how you can too.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">The Problem: AI Without a System</h2>

          <p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
            Like many professionals, I dabbled with ChatGPT when it first came out. I'd ask it questions, get responses, sometimes be impressed, sometimes be disappointed. But it wasn't until I treated AI as a productivity system—not a toy—that everything changed.
          </p>

          <p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
            The problem wasn't the AI. The problem was my approach. I was treating a Formula 1 car like a golf cart. I needed a system.
          </p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-gold-500 pl-6 py-4 my-8 bg-navy-900/50 rounded-r-lg">
            <p class="text-white text-lg italic">"The difference between dabbling with AI and mastering it isn't the tool—it's the system around it."</p>
          </blockquote>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">The Solution: A Prompt Library That Actually Works</h2>

          <p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
            I built a system of 150+ prompts, each designed for a specific task. Here's where the time savings came from:
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">1. Email Management (Saved: 3 hours/week)</h3>

          <p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
            I used to spend hours crafting emails. Now I use three simple prompts:
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-navy-400">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gold-500 mr-3">✓</span>
              <span>The "Quick Reply" prompt for routine responses</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gold-500 mr-3">✓</span>
              <span>The "Difficult Conversation" prompt for sensitive topics</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gold-500 mr-3">✓</span>
              <span>The "Executive Summary" prompt for long threads</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">2. Content Creation (Saved: 4 hours/week)</h3>

          <p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
            Blog posts, social media, newsletters—everything got faster. I use the "Content Framework" prompt to outline posts in 5 minutes instead of 45.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">3. Research & Analysis (Saved: 3 hours/week)</h3>

          <p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
            The "Competitive Analysis" prompt turns hours of research into a 10-minute task. The "Data Summary" prompt handles spreadsheet analysis I'd spend an hour on.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">4. Meeting Prep & Follow-up (Saved: 2 hours/week)</h3>

          <p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
            Pre-meeting agendas and post-meeting summaries are now automated. The "Meeting Minutes" prompt is magic.
          </p>

          <!-- Results Box -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-800 to-navy-900 rounded-2xl p-8 my-12 border border-navy-700">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The Results</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-gold-500">12</p>
                <p class="text-navy-400">Hours saved/week</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-gold-500">3x</p>
                <p class="text-navy-400">More output</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-gold-500">0</p>
                <p class="text-navy-400">Weekend work</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-gold-500">∞</p>
                <p class="text-navy-400">Hours of sanity</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">How You Can Do This Too</h2>

          <p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
            You don't need to be a tech genius. You just need a system. Here's what I recommend:
          </p>

          <ol class="space-y-4 text-navy-400 list-decimal list-inside">
            <li>
              <strong class="text-white">Start with your biggest time-wasters:</strong> What tasks take you hours but feel like they should be faster? That's your starting point.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-white">Build 3-5 core prompts:</strong> You don't need 150 on day one. Start with the prompts that solve your biggest problems.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-white">Iterate and improve:</strong> Your first prompts won't be perfect. Refine them based on results.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-white">Track your time:</strong> Measure before and after. Seeing the numbers will motivate you to expand your system.
            </li>
          </ol>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">Want the Exact Prompts I Used?</h2>

          <p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
            I've compiled my entire prompt library into the AI Productivity Suite. It includes all 150+ prompts, templates, and video walkthroughs showing exactly how to use them.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gold-500/10 border border-gold-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 my-12">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Get the AI Productivity Suite</h3>
            <p class="text-navy-400 mb-6">150+ prompts, 40+ templates, video training, and more. Start saving 10+ hours this week.</p>
            <a
              href="/product"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-gold-500 hover:bg-gold-600 text-navy-900 font-bold rounded-lg transition-colors"
            >
              Learn More
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
            The bottom line? AI isn't magic. But with the right system, it's the closest thing to a productivity superpower I've ever found.
          </p>

          <p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
            Try it for a week. Track your time. I think you'll be amazed.
          </p>
        </article>

        <!-- Article Footer -->
        <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-navy-800">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
              <span class="text-navy-400 text-sm">Share this article:</span>
              <div class="flex space-x-2">
                <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-navy-800 hover:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-navy-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M8.29 20.251c7.547 0 11.675-6.253 11.675-11.675 0-.178 0-.355-.012-.53A8.348 8.348 0 0022 5.92a8.19 8.19 0 01-2.357.646 4.118 4.118 0 001.804-2.27 8.224 8.224 0 01-2.605.996 4.107 4.107 0 00-6.993 3.743 11.65 11.65 0 01-8.457-4.287 4.106 4.106 0 001.27 5.477A4.072 4.072 0 012.8 9.713v.052a4.105 4.105 0 003.292 4.022 4.095 4.095 0 01-1.853.07 4.108 4.108 0 003.834 2.85A8.233 8.233 0 012 18.407a11.616 11.616 0 006.29 1.84" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-navy-800 hover:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-navy-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Related Posts -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-navy-900/50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Related Articles</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <article class="group">
            <a href="/blog/building-ai-workflow-guide" class="block">
              <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-800 to-navy-700 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-4xl">🛠️</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors">Building Your AI Workflow: A Step-by-Step Guide</h3>
              <p class="text-navy-400 text-sm mt-2">Tutorial • 12 min read</p>
            </a>
          </article>

          <article class="group">
            <a href="/blog/5-prompts-every-marketer-needs" class="block">
              <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-800 to-navy-700 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-4xl">📢</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors">The 5 Prompts Every Marketer Needs in 2026</h3>
              <p class="text-navy-400 text-sm mt-2">Marketing • 6 min read</p>
            </a>
          </article>

          <article class="group">
            <a href="/blog/why-people-fail-ai-productivity" class="block">
              <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-800 to-navy-700 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-4xl">🎯</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors">Why Most People Fail at AI Productivity</h3>
              <p class="text-navy-400 text-sm mt-2">Strategy • 10 min read</p>
            </a>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
